  "original_title": "\u0bb5\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0bb8\u0bcd\u0b85\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd   \u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Menstruation on WhatsApp",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Various processors have come up these days to remind us to record menstrual information for women.",
        "In this case, the WhatsApp processor to know the information related to this and monitor the health of the body. Has introduced a new feature.",
        "The woman was told on her phone to send a \"Hi\" message to the business WhatsApp account number Sirona `+ 9718866644` and then answer any questions that may be asked.",
        "It has also been reported that they will be able to know, verify, remind and monitor their menstrual details every month if they provide details."
      ],
      "title_ents": [
        {
          "text": "WhatsApp",
          "label": "ORG"
        }
      ],
      "body_line_ents_list": [
        [],
        [
